Package net.hudup.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BatchScript
    This utility class helps users to retrieve a dataset pool and a list of algorithm names from text batch script for evaluating many datasets and many algorithms later.
    DatasetSampler
    Utility class for sampling dataset.
    DatasetUtil2
    This is the second utility class for processing dataset.
    DefaultExternalQuery
    This class is default implementation of ExternalQuery interface.
    MapVector<T>
    This class is a map of general-type elements but it represents a (rating) vector having identifier.
    ProviderImpl
    This class is the default implementation of Provider to process dataset.
    ScannerImpl
    This class is the default implementation of Scanner.
    SemiScanner
    This class represents a semi-scanner which is a scanner but store frequent-access rating matrix in memory.
    SnapshotImpl
    This class is the default implementation of Snapshot.
